subtitle: nangsư̄ ʻanusō̜n nư̄ang nai warōkāt thī --Phana-- Sattrāčhān Sanyā Thammasak mī ʻāyu 84 pī bō̜ribūn, wan thī 5 Mēsāyon 2534.
title: "Pūchanīyabukkhon bǣpchabap"

notes.value:
PRIORITY 3.
In Thai.
Cover title: --Phana-- Sattrāčhān Sanyā Thammasak, "pūchanīyabukkhon bǣpchabap".
"Phim pen ʻanusō̜n nai ʻōkāt ʻāyu khrop 84 pī, wan thī 5 Mēsāyon Phutthasakkarāt 2534"--cover.
Commemorative volume brought out on the 84th birth anniversary of Sanyā Thammasak, b. 1907, a former Thai prime minister and president of the Privy Council; comprises contributed articles on his life and work.
